{"tid":117963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人結婚冇擺酒？","createTime":"2017-02-12T15:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T15:57:51.000Z","uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07f8def1a82eb28fa4bd330e7fd0352b8fbd57df","tid":117963,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"最近開始考慮結婚 但又唔想擺酒<br />\n第一冇錢 第二唔想擺場大龍鳳俾錢人賺<br />\n最擔心係啲老人家唔鍾意唔擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3b8f8c5ba347351b68422a6bb3cbf7ec5e3152","tid":117963,"uid":27212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"擺酒係唔會用你太多錢。<br />\n因為一來一回你可以拎返，最大支出反而係影相，同其他野。"},{"pid":"089d00df9ad885d7a932658cecfb885e619cd5bf","tid":117963,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"你都未撚同班長老傾<br />\n上網問有春用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aaa5adb3b4d284caf350fa4447797f5a46f3fb1","tid":117963,"uid":76005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"擺場細細地嘅酒"},{"pid":"bf06358b14d1ae6237edb1acc841800e44d01cd0","tid":117963,"uid":27212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"仲有，計埋金器你仲有機會賺。<br />\n<br />\n你話唔想攪咁多野，咁大家願意咪唔好攪，簽個名咪算囉。 最緊要你老婆都同意。"},{"pid":"ef5a68b854519caff3b230752331554bfe7172e9","tid":117963,"uid":27212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都未撚同班長老傾<br />\n上網問有春用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意！"},{"pid":"29d2c9ce3b673105364cfa81b1416e562d89ca99","tid":117963,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都未撚同班長老傾<br />\n上網問有春用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意！</blockquote><br />\n想睇下有冇人會分享下被迫擺酒或者勸得掂長老嘅經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋見到之前有個同事擺酒 好似好多野搞好麻煩"}]}